Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.83,0:00:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.64,NarTop,,0,0,50,,Hey there, Junpei here again.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.28,NarTop,,0,0,50,,My first foray into
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.70,NarTop,,0,0,50,,major motion pictures ended in a big hit.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.70,0:01:06.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now, we're in the middle of secretly filming our next AV production. {probably secret here means they haven't reserved the train or anything}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.10,Top,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.73,0:01:16.14,Top,,0,0,0,,Good, now let's do another take of running through the {train }car.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.14,0:01:19.96,Top,,0,0,0,,This time, run all the way to the front and get cornered by the thug.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.56,Top,,0,0,0,,Let's do it without rehearsing.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of course, there was no way we could get permission,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,so we shot everything guerrilla-style.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At least it's going well for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.97,0:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.67,0:01:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.70,0:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What the hell are you guys\N doing on my train?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Or not.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, get the Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.72,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait for me, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Junpei! Equipment! Our equipment!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw me the tripod already! {nc}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.76,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice catch.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.23,0:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How cruel!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For the millionth time,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.64,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we were making a film called \N"Romantic Journey on Private Railway Lines." {私鉄線ロマンの旅}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.02,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Romantic Journey on Private Railway Lines"\N sounds like an innocent film. {no clue what's this kankyou, could be "government permission; official license video" but I'm only finding environmental videos; feels like I'm missing something here, it's not in the manga either; was "tourist" in voldemort's TL but I don't trust him}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.52,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there a half-naked girl\N in such an innocent film?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.54,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We just thought it would be nice\N to include a pretty girl in it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.36,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Works for me. \NI like it better when there's a cute girl too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.07,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But a bare-breasted or even a fully naked girl is going too far!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.51,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something called common morality.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't even bother getting a permit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were with\N Apollo Productions, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.04,0:03:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Their president said they've never heard of anyone with your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei Junpei?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have an employee\N by that name.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.66,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In your position, it's better to tell the truth\N now so we can all can go home sooner.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! Now I'm fucking pissed!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.61,0:04:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept my mouth shut until the end \Nfor everyone's sake!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.48,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Koganei Junpei? Nah, we don't have any employees by that name."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.53,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I've been working\N so hard if you do that to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.51,0:04:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really, they went home already?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.06,0:04:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all so cold to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Koganei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're Director Shibuya's secretary.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here so late?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.37,0:04:47.53,Top,,0,0,0,,I... I came here to ask a favor of you, Koganei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.05,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun is probably really mad right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun, nice work!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we abandoned you today.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.92,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorr... What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You horny, hard-on pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The second I let you out of my sight, you do {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's not what you think! {/a misunderstanding}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it wasn't what you thought!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.08,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's my fault for causing all this commotion.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need your help too, Wakaba-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please star me in your next adult video.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.73,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't... Isn't it strange\N that I'm still a virgin at age 20?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.97,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had any luck with men since\N a traumatic experience I had as a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.29,0:06:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I just can't figure out how to conduct myself around men. {lit: can't receive/accept/agree with men - w/e she means}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was hoping
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.28,0:06:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that maybe if I was with Koganei-kun, \NI could manage to lose my virginity happily.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to be in our adult video for that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.87,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ogawa-san will be any good.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.44,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a decent-sized chest and,\N even more importantly, she has guts.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.34,0:06:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the chief will like her. Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that was really moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.27,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you coming back for me and all...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.85,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourself. I just came back to collect something I forgot.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty cold, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.32,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I endured hours of lecturing in that nasty stationmaster's office,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking that I'm doing it for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a word of thanks?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is actually \Nvery grateful to you, Junpei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.68,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you hadn't taken the fall\N for everyone back there,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.54,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they would've confiscated the tape,\N and we'd've had to scrap the project.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You also saved all of our equipment.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that the tape and equipment are more important than me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. It's a fact of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, get inside me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun, hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You never learn, do you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel! {nc}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.49,0:08:22.46,Top,,0,0,0,,You see, in essence, adult videos are sort of like fresh fruits. {perishable foods; perishables}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.96,Top,,0,0,0,,The fresher and spicier the girls are, the better.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.31,0:08:33.73,Top,,0,0,0,,Like, for example, a girl who says,\N"You're kiwi, papaya, and mango." {referencing https://lyricstranslate.com/en/kimi-tachi-kiwi%E3%83%BBpapaya%E3%83%BBmango-da-ne-youre-kiwi-papaya-and.html}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.73,0:08:35.13,Top,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Chief?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.13,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yeah, that's... Right. \NThis is where you come in, Koganei.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your duty for today \Nis to find Apollo's next star.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.20,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In Harajuku, Shibuya, and Roppongi, we'll be scouting out powerful and exciting girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Chief...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.86,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Miwa-san and I have\N already found the perfect girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that? \NYou already found someone?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're just doing your thing again, you horndog.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Horndog! Rake!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.14,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just stealing everything\N I wanted to say!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.12,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to keep you shut for a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.77,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei, you've done it!\N You've done well!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hearing that from you is reassuring... {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.03,0:09:33.90,Top,,0,0,0,,Junpei-chan, when did you trick her\N into joining? Hurry up and introduce us!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.28,Top,,0,0,0,,I also can't wait to meet her!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What's she like?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's anything like Diane Lane,\N I'll die a happy man! {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diane_Lane}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.36,0:09:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I guess there {\i1}is{\i0} a certain resemblance...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If only a little, Junpei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Are you serious? \NWhere is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my Diane Lane-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Those sexy legs!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.60,0:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho-ho! Those tantalizing hips!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.88,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! That chest is the real deal!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And most crucially, her face...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.02,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Diane Lane! Look! Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. \NI'm Ogawa Masako.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei, she's no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, she doesn't look like Diane Lane.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She does look a little like her, \Ndoesn't she? Maybe her hair...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she doesn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Still, that's no reason to turn her down!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! You're being rude to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.16,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my job. I have to leave concerns\N about rudeness or whatever else behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.25,0:10:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Do I really look that bland to you? {/unappealing}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really so hopeless?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to tell you \Nwhy you're no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Try fucking Koganei on my desk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. Lie down.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it together, won't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.46,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all part of the job, \Nisn't it, Miwa-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.33,0:12:36.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's totally faking it. \NShe's not turned on at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.96,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... I'm just... I'm no good!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.23,0:12:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa-kun, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.93,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a virgin, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your smell.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait... {chotto}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's about to suck me in.{only hear "suikomare"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.68,0:12:59.56,Overlap,,0,0,0,,No! Not that kind of smell!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.56,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I always play that "Virgin Search" game in magazines,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and so far, I haven't been wrong even once. {a section that run in the men's journal "Weekly Jewel" from 1981 to 1996; in it, they printed the gravures of a dozen girls and you had to guess by the photo alone whether she was a virgin or not - the results were printed on a separate page; more info: https://www.zakzak.co.jp/entertainment/ent-news/news/20150715/enn1507150830010-n1.htm}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Chief, are you suggesting Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of our business!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's one more reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One more?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.41,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know it yourself \Nbetter than anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.37,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Still, Chief, why can't we record Ogawa's first time with Koganei-kun on video?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.20,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment a girl changes into a woman\N is the most beautiful her body will ever be!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we do it, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say no, that's final.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit! Give me a real reason!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei-san, Miwa-san, \NI've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.96,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.82,0:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all that about, Chief?! \NExplain yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.06,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit, she {\i1}does{\i0} have something special about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not film her?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's too gloomy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.13,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want to capture is\N the carefree brightness of today.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Video has no need\N for wet blankets! {nekura = dark-natured; gloomy; dour; moody; insular; glum; pessimistic​}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the only reason\N why you won't take her?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.81,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover yourself before going outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! G-Good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.57,Song,,0,0,0,,Where are you from? {https://www.mamalisa.com/?t=es&p=3176}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.70,Song,,0,0,0,,From Higo
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.56,Song,,0,0,0,,Where in Higo?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.23,Song,,0,0,0,,From Kumamoto
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.44,Song,,0,0,0,,Where in Kumamoto?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.00,Song,,0,0,0,,From Senba
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.00,0:14:46.36,Song,,0,0,0,,In the mountains of Senba,\Nthere is a raccoon
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.36,0:14:50.24,Song,,0,0,0,,A hunter shot it with a gun
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.93,Song,,0,0,0,,He cooked it, then roasted it and ate it
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.62,0:14:57.85,Song,,0,0,0,,He covered it with leaves from a tree
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't dwell on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like me \Nto get discouraged by this.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, chin up!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Blended whisky.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.71,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't order that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from that lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I was waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was{\i0} waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you no longer expect them to come. {/already given up on them coming}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.88,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily. The one I was waiting for \Nis sitting next to me right now. {lit: before my eyes - hence ujiki is looking around}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, \NPresident Ujiki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know my name?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember now? \NAt your office yesterday. {nc whats kinou no ***}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seducing you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.87,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you said I have no appeal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came here to seduce you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that funny?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think\N an inexperienced girl like you
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.46,0:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,can seduce a seasoned man like me,\N who's been around the block? {cunning and experienced in the ways of the world; crafty and worldly-wise; sly old (fox)​}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I succeed?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it. Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna bet?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet? F-Fine by me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.92,0:17:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, you'll star me in your next video.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I win?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.48,0:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dance naked at the Shinjuku Hokoten. {https://janejacobsjapan.com/2017/09/04/hokoten/#:~:text=Shinjuku%20(%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%BF3,meters%20(~2%2C400%20feet).}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt you'll really \Nbe able to seduce me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll show you otherwise.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver, to Ichigaya please.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My apartment.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.34,0:17:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,First, she threatens to seduce me, \Nthen she makes me wait for ages!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.93,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is the aroma of a home-cooked meal \Nthat'd make any bachelor cry with joy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut the pickles now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.73,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.89,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with this silly charade. \NHave a fun night with Uncle Ujiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.28,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I won the bet.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The bet?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.99,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd say something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this?! The hell! {nc}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me down! Let me down!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's me down!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got it all on tape!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Infallible proof!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now. You were all in cahoots \Nto put one over on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.91,0:19:19.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, the video of Masako's defloration was now in the works.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.69,0:19:25.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I was struggling mightily \Nwith the screenplay. {hard fighting; hard struggle; fighting against heavy odds}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.78,0:19:29.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The location was already set, \Nso it became a vacation romance story. {lit: place that is cool in the summer; place one goes to escape the heat of summer; summer retreat​ - think he means the "vacation roman" genre}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,I live for moments like these...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako-san, you seem in high spirits.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.68,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something nice happen to you recently?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you answer the phone for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.76,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. See you later, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. Take your time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.48,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this warmth!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Masako's smell!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.13,Top,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.37,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bad news, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.68,Top,,0,0,0,,It's Koganei!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.30,Top,,0,0,0,,It's that bastard Koganei!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.30,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's putting my secretary in a porno?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it. I'll never let him!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.43,0:20:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa-kun, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Help me, Koganei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then zoom in there, got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like she left a while ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must be up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.40,0:21:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the type of girl to cancel\N a meeting without warning.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.90,0:21:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she didn't get in an accident.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.46,0:21:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and have a look.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.37,0:21:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. It's not supposed to be their day off.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It just got even stranger.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.07,0:22:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Could she be here?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.74,0:23:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I knew it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.65,0:23:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.49,0:23:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What have they done to you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come help you right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.53,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it together... {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.26,0:23:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei!
