Dialogue: 10,0:36:33.06,0:36:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:36.73,0:36:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Get away from me!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.80,0:36:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa-san, watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:40.71,0:36:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei! Fucking move it! \NGive my Masako-san back!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:44.52,0:36:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:46.68,0:36:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't move,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:47.74,0:36:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll make you!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:51.20,0:36:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy crackers! It melted the iron!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:54.20,0:36:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:55.31,0:36:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Koganei! Can't you see it?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:06.47,0:37:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The stuff of legends—the red thread!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:08.88,0:37:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:10.29,0:37:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.43,0:37:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:19.35,0:37:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's going to be the first real fuck \NI've seen in a long time!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:25.35,0:37:27.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:27.24,0:37:32.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,I used to reject men firmly for so long, \Nbut now I seem to be losing strength.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.78,0:37:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gondo, you're dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:34.52,0:37:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how you repay my kindness?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:37.65,0:37:40.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,Director, it's okay now.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:40.24,0:37:46.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,I know you've been extremely careful to avoid triggering my traumatic childhood experience.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:51.17,0:37:55.70,Song,,0,0,0,,In the mountains of Senba,\Nthere is a raccoon
Dialogue: 10,0:37:55.70,0:37:59.58,Song,,0,0,0,,A hunter shot it with a gun
Dialogue: 10,0:37:59.58,0:38:03.05,Song,,0,0,0,,He cooked it, then roasted it and ate it
Dialogue: 10,0:38:03.05,0:38:07.08,Song,,0,0,0,,He covered it with leaves from a tree...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:28.09,0:38:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this gentle, nostalgic feeling that strikes me right in the heart? {no clue what's this sobako}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:33.37,0:38:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's love! It's love!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:36.30,0:38:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa-kun, you kids taught me something. It's love!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:40.68,0:38:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the necessary ingredient of real sex!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:46.02,0:38:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:49.51,0:38:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:54.60,0:38:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:56.74,0:38:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You feel great.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:01.43,0:39:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:03.20,0:39:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, you're awake?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.88,0:39:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God! I was so worried about you!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:08.09,0:39:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about you take your thing away from me! {lit: Get that lower half out of the way.}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:11.13,0:39:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud! I let my guard down for a second, and this is what happens!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:15.80,0:39:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You goddamn horny hard-on pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:16.40,0:39:17.31,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ah... No, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:19.06,0:39:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not what you think! {/as misunderstanding}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:21.93,0:39:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was this video that brought the two of them together.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:26.41,0:39:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even rewatching it now\N still moves me deeply.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.44,0:39:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa Masako's mother was my Madonna \Nwhen I was just an assistant director. {probably means "mistress/nymph"}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:35.57,0:39:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally was able to make good \Non my promise to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:40.06,0:39:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it felt to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:42.73,0:39:47.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end, that guerrilla AV\N became a major hit.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:47.63,0:39:51.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as a result of it,\N Gondo-san and Ogawa-san got married.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:52.15,0:39:55.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I've never been to a wedding before.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:55.98,0:39:59.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Miwa-san and I will also end up married one day, heh.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:03.76,0:40:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ, Koganei!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:05.58,0:40:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}There's a time and a place\N to get hard, you numbskull! {/to get hard at a place like this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.72,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sexy Cat wo-o-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:30.64,English,,0,0,0,,I met you at a party {by some miracle, I found a CD booklet with lyrics; Welcome My Sexy Cat Woh \NPartyで出逢った \NWelcome My Sweet Cat Woh \NJeans の妖精 \N「送らせてよ」と追いかけていった Motor Pool \Nサイド・シートに下心を乗せて \NWho/ だけどRadio から bad news ムードは sold out ジョークだけで\Nスゥイッチ・オン My heart, it's all right/\NWelcome My Sexy Cat Woh \N悪戯な光る瞳 \NWelcome My Sweet Cat Woh \N最高のタイプさ\Nとりとめのない やりとり交わす 湾岸 Road \N「12:00迄には送ってネ･･･」とささやく\N聞こえないフリで演じるぜ コメディー\N時計なんか外させたい\N矢継ぎ早の trick/trick/trick/trick/\NWelcome My Sexy Cat \Nまるで "Marie claire" のF.G. ページ \NWelcome My Sweet Cat Woh \NN*19 誘うぜ \NWho/time up 告げる時報 \N12:00まであと少しさ\Nスゥイッチ・オフ radio, it's all right}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:33.72,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sweet Cat wo-o-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.67,English,,0,0,0,,A fairy in jeans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:42.27,English,,0,0,0,,I chased you to the motor pool, "Let me walk you home"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:47.96,English,,0,0,0,,Putting my ulterior motives on the side seat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:54.04,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa, but the radio is giving me bad news
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:57.25,English,,0,0,0,,My mood is sold out, you're only joking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.69,English,,0,0,0,,Switch on my heart, it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:03.76,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Welcome My Sexy Cat wo-o-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.82,0:40:27.16,English,,0,0,0,,Asphalt, the lonely building {same booklet; アスファルト 孤独のビルディング\N立ちすくむ 見慣れた都会\N時の流れに背中を押され\N生きるのも悪くはないさだけど\N\N作り笑いの パズリング・デイズ\N過ごしたくないだけなのさ\N\Nターミナル 仮面の群れを\N眺め疲れて コンコース歩いてみる\Nあと少しで P.M.5: 00 o'clock \Nworking time 脱け出せるけど\N\N出口は無いさ バズリング・テイズ\N独り 明日へ向かう \N\NJust a puzzle 合わす様に\Nリスキーなまま生きてくしかない \N"現実"に Never say no/\N\N作り笑いの バズリング・デイズ\N過したくないからさ \N\NIt's a puzzle 合わす様に\Nリスキーなまま生きてくしかない \N"現実"に Never say no/}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.37,0:40:34.26,English,,0,0,0,,Standing frozen in the familiar city
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.26,0:40:40.44,English,,0,0,0,,Pushed by the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.77,0:40:48.46,English,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad to be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.46,0:41:00.66,English,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to spend\N these puzzling days faking a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.12,0:41:07.88,English,,0,0,0,,Tired of looking at a crowd of masks
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.90,0:41:16.89,English,,0,0,0,,At the terminal, I walk down the concourse
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.72,0:41:20.93,English,,0,0,0,,It's almost
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.13,0:41:25.04,English,,0,0,0,,5 o'clock PM
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.64,0:41:30.43,English,,0,0,0,,I can escape from my working time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.19,0:41:35.09,English,,0,0,0,,But there's no way out of the puzzling days
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:41.85,English,,0,0,0,,I'm alone, heading toward tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.70,0:41:48.60,English,,0,0,0,,Just a puzzle that I have to piece together
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.60,0:41:55.94,English,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to live riskily
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.94,0:42:03.35,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.58,0:42:42.42,English,,0,0,0,,I don't want to spend\N these puzzling days faking a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.23,0:42:49.18,English,,0,0,0,,It's a puzzle that I have to piece together
