Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.44,0:43:00.46,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.46,0:43:05.75,English,,0,0,0,,A puzzle that I have to piece together
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.75,0:43:13.26,English,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to live riskily
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.26,0:43:21.50,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to reality!
